{"tid":1462991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再推垃圾文","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:31:47.000Z","uid":197989,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d508b10331f19ab6852ee62147fe8543b761283","tid":1462991,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"轉發:一名政府人員的看法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n鬼唔撚知玩象棋要將死對面<br />\n問題人地前面有車馬炮士象卒<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求最重要係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真雙普選大家都知</strong></span><br />\n無知d都有聽過民間第1日記招啦<br />\n依家有個所謂政府高官出黎出篇文就打晒飛機?<br />\n<br />\n撤回=暫緩? <br />\n呢樣野打左幾耐兩樣野唔同<br />\n成班食懞左?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對得住死左嘅義士?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n外國認為bill is dead?<br />\n大家呢排睇左幾多新聞外媒報香港嘅事<br />\n幾時見到有人認為示威者錯晒?<br />\n依家連美國兩會都撐緊我地<br />\n你返返去話外國支持不足?<br />\n<br />\n覺得打交唔夠警察打<br />\n但就認為可以用司法對抗呢個佢聲稱嘅合法暴力團體?<br />\n有無帶腦出街?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用監警會呀?<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好見到1,2個點似同路人<br />\n就<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捆綁式</span></strong>推晒成篇文<br />\n根本篇野毫無價值<br />\n睇完, 方法呢?<br />\n<br />\n邊有人捉棋第1步要將軍?<br />\n最後係要, 但你唔拎走d卒點將軍?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">隨時比人一隻車車撚死你</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09fb877e3c4ba83753199cbf0a975d5396f785f","tid":1462991,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"自推10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嬲撚到呢"},{"pid":"fbd8560af13522cbe5701c28726410ed95101725","tid":1462991,"uid":290285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:52:28.000Z","msg":"認同 幫推"},{"pid":"6dbebb4e4694524f2cc69641526afe5034a7ee80","tid":1462991,"uid":197989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"2"},{"